Working script for Linux (Tested Only on Ubuntu)

Program to add a context menu entry "Download Subtitle" on right clicking a video file.

Need to install nautilus-actions package
sudo apt-get install nautilus-actions

1. Context Menu entry provided by nautilus-actions
2. On clicking 'Download Subtitle' getSUB.py is called to download the sub from opensubtitles.org

